WEBVTT

00:01:57.320 --> 00:02:00.376
But that was not the worst.

00:02:00.400 --> 00:02:04.520
It got even worse
than I could have ever imagined.

00:02:05.920 --> 00:02:07.520
I got arrested,

00:02:08.440 --> 00:02:10.576
maliciously charged

00:02:10.600 --> 00:02:11.840
and prosecuted.

00:02:14.440 --> 00:02:19.016
The absurdity of it all
was the arresting officer

00:02:19.040 --> 00:02:24.176
asking me to pay him 10,000 US dollars

00:02:24.200 --> 00:02:26.480
and the case would disappear.

00:02:27.840 --> 00:02:29.040
I refused.